From 2017, all 3T products have a unique serial number using a new format. This ensures you have a genuine 3T product.

If you register your product here, you qualify for:

* Extended warranty on select items (details in the Warranty Policy)

* Discount of 30% on cost of replacement if your product is damaged beyond repair by a crash

You’ll receive a confirmation of your registration and any benefits you qualify for by email.

  • Reset

    WHERE DO I FIND MY SERIAL NUMBER?

    From January 2017 all the product delivered have the S/N below the QR code.

    WHEELS

    For Orbis II and Discus wheels, the serial number is placed on the rim, under the rim tape.

    FRAMES

    For Exploro frames, we have different versions of the serial number.

    CASE A - Warranty Card
    The serial number is included in a longer string of characters that includes also the product model. The serial number are the last 9 characters of the string, starting with VV. You can scan also the QR code to read the S/N.

    CASE B - On the frame
    The serial number is applied under the bottom bracket, on a silver sticker
